{"timestamp":"2026-05-28T01:40:36.803Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"edit","args":{"filePath":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/package.json","oldString":"  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"test\": \"jest\",\n    \"prepublishOnly\": \"npm run build\"\n  },","newString":"  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"test\": \"jest\",\n    \"prepublishOnly\": \"npm run build\",\n    \"setup:local\": \"mkdir -p .opencode/agents && ln -sf ../../agents/mdocs-orchestrator.md .opencode/agents/mdocs-orchestrator.md\"\n  },"}}}
{"timestamp":"2026-05-28T01:40:43.127Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"read","args":{"filePath":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/README.md","limit":60}}}
{"timestamp":"2026-05-28T01:40:58.557Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"edit","args":{"filePath":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/README.md","oldString":"### For Local Development (Dogfooding)\n\nWhen working on the plugin itself, opencode loads it directly from the built output:\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run build\n```\n\nCreate `opencode.json` in the project root:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"https://opencode.ai/config.json\",\n  \"plugin\": [\"./dist/index.js\"]\n}\n```\n\nThe plugin automatically registers the `mdocs-orchestrator` agent and skills directory on load.","newString":"### For Local Development (Dogfooding)\n\nWhen working on the plugin itself, opencode loads it directly from the built output:\n\n```bash\nnpm install\nnpm run build\nnpm run setup:local\n```\n\nThe `setup:local` script creates a symlink in `.opencode/agents/` pointing to the package's agent file. This is required because opencode discovers agents at startup (before the plugin's config hook runs).\n\nCreate `opencode.json` in the project root:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"https://opencode.ai/config.json\",\n  \"plugin\": [\"./dist/index.js\"]\n}\n```"}}}
