{"timestamp":"2026-05-28T01:41:41.982Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"bash","args":{"command":"git commit -m \"fix(dogfooding): restore local agent discovery with symlink\n\nThe .opencode/agents/ copy was removed to avoid duplicate sources of truth,\nbut this broke local development because opencode discovers agents at startup\nbefore the plugin's config hook runs.\n\n- Add .opencode/agents/mdocs-orchestrator.md as a symlink to ./agents/\n- Update .gitignore to ignore runtime files but keep the symlink\n- Add npm run setup:local script to create the symlink\n- Update README with clear local dev instructions\n\nThis maintains:\n- Single source of truth: ./agents/mdocs-orchestrator.md\n- Local dev works: opencode discovers agent from .opencode/agents/\n- Consumer setup works: config hook auto-registers from npm package path\n\nTests: 88/88 passing\" && git push origin main","description":"Commit and push dogfooding fix","workdir":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs","timeout":120000}}}
