{"timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:33:17.891Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"bash","args":{"command":"gh pr create --title \"feat: align implementation with philosophy — Phase 1\" --body '## Summary\n\nImplements Phase 1 of the philosophy alignment roadmap: four incremental slices that make the existing mdocs model clearly embody the distributed shared memory philosophy without large rewrites.\n\n## Changes\n\n### 1. v2 Initiative/Wiki Memory Metadata (`97e412a`)\n- Initiative: `phase`, `handoffSummary`, `openQuestions`, `blockers`, `nextAction`\n- Wiki: `lifecycle`, `knowledgeType`, `confidence`, `sourceInitiatives`, `supersedes`\n- Backward-compatible — v1 files continue to parse without errors\n\n### 2. Enriched Dispatch Memory Retrieval (`77d6cdc`)\n- `SearchResult` extended with `snippet` and `matchedFields`\n- `SubagentAssembler` produces enriched context: handoff summary, blockers, progress, retrieved memory, recent activity\n- `mdocs_dispatch` now queries search engine and audit log automatically\n\n### 3. Resume/Status Cockpit (`9898499`)\n- `WorkflowEngine.setActiveInitiative()` and `resumeAt()` for workflow control\n- New `mdocs_resume` tool: next action, blockers, latest progress, validation\n- `mdocs_status` enriched with `resume` object for active initiative\n\n### 4. Cross-Link Graph Linter (`e588dab`)\n- Graph-level lint: broken initiative↔wiki links, missing backlinks, done initiative completion gates\n- `mdocs_validate` includes graph results\n\n### 5. Documentation (`a8ed2ab`)\n- Skills updated (mdocs-workflow, mdocs-initiative) with v2 fields and resume-first flow\n- Roadmap wiki updated with Phase 1 implementation notes\n- Gap analysis wiki updated with closed gaps\n- All 4 Phase 1 sub-initiatives marked done\n\n## Verification\n\n- **Tests:** 122 passed (baseline 113 → +9 new), 11 suites, 0 failures\n- **Build:** TypeScript compiles cleanly\n- **Pack:** `npm pack --dry-run` succeeds\n- **TDD:** Every behavior change has RED → GREEN evidence\n\n## Related\n\n- Initiative: `align-implementation-with-philosophy`\n- Sub-initiatives: `define-v2-memory-metadata`, `upgrade-dispatch-memory-retrieval`, `add-resume-status-cockpit`, `add-cross-link-graph-linter` (all marked done)\n' --base main 2>&1","description":"Create pull request","workdir":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs"}}}
