{"timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:49:16.044Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"bash","args":{"command":"gh api repos/bbaaxx/opencode-mdocs/pulls/2/reviews/4392366338/comments -f body=\"All five items addressed in 0892438:\n\n**🔴 graph validation filtering** — Fixed. \\`validationResult()\\` now separates file-quality results (\\`file !== \\\"GRAPH\\\"\\`) from graph-level results. File-quality lint errors no longer make \\`mdocs_validate.graph.valid\\` false.\n\n**🔴 YAML array parsing** — Fixed. Extracted shared \\`parseYamlValue()\\` and \\`parseFrontmatter()\\` into \\`types.ts\\`, used by \\`linter.ts\\`, \\`initiative.ts\\`, and \\`wiki.ts\\`. Handles both JSON arrays (\\`[\\\"a\\\",\\\"b\\\"]\\`) and YAML inline arrays (\\`[a, b, c]\\`). Verified against all 30 initiative files and 9 wiki files in the repo — all parse correctly now. 15 new tests.\n\n**🟡 v2 field mappings** — Fixed. \\`initiative.create\\` accepts phase, handoffSummary, openQuestions, blockers, nextAction. \\`initiative.update\\` accepts all v2 fields. \\`wiki.create\\` accepts lifecycle, knowledgeType, confidence, sourceInitiatives, supersedes.\n\n**🟡 status/resume acceptance gaps** — Fixed. \\`mdocs_status\\` now includes lastActivity (from audit log), currentPlanItem, staleWarning (flagged when >3 days since update), and per-initiative nextAction/blockers. \\`mdocs_resume\\` without an initiativeId returns all resumable active initiatives with recommendations (ready/blocked/stale).\n\n**🟡 README docs** — Fixed. Documents all 8 custom tools including mdocs_resume, mdocs_validate, mdocs_lookup, and enriched mdocs_dispatch.\n\nVerification: 137 tests pass (was 122), build clean, pack clean.\" 2>&1","description":"Reply to PR review","workdir":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs"}}}
{"timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:49:26.906Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"bash","args":{"command":"gh pr comment 2 --body \"All five review items addressed in 0892438:\n\n**🔴 graph validation filtering** — Fixed. \\`validationResult()\\` now separates file-quality results (\\`file !== \\\"GRAPH\\\"\\`) from graph-level results. File-quality lint errors no longer make \\`mdocs_validate.graph.valid\\` false.\n\n**🔴 YAML array parsing** — Fixed. Extracted shared \\`parseYamlValue()\\` and \\`parseFrontmatter()\\` into \\`types.ts\\`, used by \\`linter.ts\\`, \\`initiative.ts\\`, and \\`wiki.ts\\`. Handles both JSON arrays (\\`[\\\"a\\\",\\\"b\\\"]\\`) and YAML inline arrays (\\`[a, b, c]\\`). Verified against all 30 initiative files and 9 wiki files — all parse correctly now. 15 new tests.\n\n**🟡 v2 field mappings** — Fixed. \\`initiative.create\\` accepts phase, handoffSummary, openQuestions, blockers, nextAction. \\`initiative.update\\` accepts all v2 fields. \\`wiki.create\\` accepts lifecycle, knowledgeType, confidence, sourceInitiatives, supersedes.\n\n**🟡 status/resume acceptance gaps** — Fixed. \\`mdocs_status\\` now includes lastActivity (from audit log), currentPlanItem, staleWarning (flagged when >3 days since update), and per-initiative nextAction/blockers. \\`mdocs_resume\\` without an initiativeId returns all resumable active initiatives with recommendations (ready/blocked/stale).\n\n**🟡 README docs** — Fixed. Documents all 8 custom tools including mdocs_resume, mdocs_validate, mdocs_lookup, and enriched mdocs_dispatch.\n\nVerification: 137 tests pass (was 122), build clean, pack clean.\" --repo bbaaxx/opencode-mdocs 2>&1","description":"Comment on PR with fix summary","workdir":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs"}}}
