{"timestamp":"2026-05-29T20:29:07.177Z","type":"tool","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"task","args":{"description":"Verify implementation matches plan","subagent_type":"explore","prompt":"I need to verify that the Phase 1 implementation of the \"Align Implementation with Philosophy\" initiative is correctly implemented in the codebase. Thoroughness: very thorough.\n\nCheck the following source files and confirm each feature is present:\n\n**Task 1: v2 metadata** — Check `src/types.ts` for optional fields: `phase`, `handoffSummary`, `openQuestions`, `blockers`, `nextAction` on Initiative type, and `lifecycle`, `knowledgeType`, `confidence`, `sourceInitiatives`, `supersedes` on WikiEntry type. Check `src/initiative.ts` for write/parse of these fields. Check `src/wiki.ts` for write/parse of wiki v2 fields.\n\n**Task 2: Dispatch memory retrieval** — Check `src/types.ts` for `snippet` and `matchedFields` on SearchResult. Check `src/search.ts` for snippet generation. Check `src/subagent.ts` for enriched assembly with options parameter (retrievedMemory, recentEvents) and sections: Handoff Summary, Next Action, Blockers, Retrieved Memory, Recent Activity. Check `src/plugin.ts` for enriched mdocs_dispatch that queries search and audit.\n\n**Task 3: Resume cockpit** — Check `src/workflow.ts` for `setActiveInitiative()` and `resumeAt()` methods. Check `src/plugin.ts` for `mdocs_resume` custom tool.\n\n**Task 4: Graph linter** — Check `src/linter.ts` for `lintAll()` method and graph linting logic (backlinks, missing references, done initiative stable wiki check). Check `src/plugin.ts` for graph results in mdocs_validate.\n\nReturn a structured report with:\n- For each task: what was found vs what was expected\n- Any gaps or missing implementations\n- Overall assessment: PASS or FAIL"}}}
