{"timestamp":"2026-05-31T23:37:34.543Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"prepare-v1-1-0-release","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"apply_patch","args":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/package.json\n@@\n-  \"version\": \"1.0.2\",\n+  \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n@@\n   \"files\": [\n     \"dist\",\n     \"skills\",\n     \"agents\",\n-    \"templates\"\n+    \"templates\",\n+    \"CHANGELOG.md\"\n   ]\n }\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/package-lock.json\n@@\n-  \"version\": \"1.0.2\",\n+  \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n@@\n-      \"version\": \"1.0.2\",\n+      \"version\": \"1.1.0\",\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/CHANGELOG.md\n@@\n and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).\n \n+## [1.1.0] - 2026-05-31\n+\n+### Added\n+\n+- Added aggregate `mdocs` custom tool for initiative and wiki operations, including create/update/done/archive/delete/list, validation, and index sync commands.\n+- Added `mdocs_validate`, `mdocs_lookup`, and `mdocs_resume` tools for integrity checks, exact initiative resolution, and workflow handoff recovery.\n+- Expanded `mdocs_dispatch` context with search-ranked memory, recent audit events, blockers, handoff metadata, and related wiki context.\n+- Added wiki/initiative graph validation for broken references, missing backlinks, and completion-gate warnings.\n+\n+### Changed\n+\n+- Improved README tool documentation to reflect the full current custom tool surface.\n+- Included `CHANGELOG.md` in published package contents.\n+\n+### Fixed\n+\n+- Wrapped custom tool results in object shapes expected by opencode custom tool contracts.\n+- Updated the integration smoke script to validate the current `plugin.tool` API.\n+\n ## [1.0.2] - 2026-05-28\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/README.md\n@@\n The plugin provides custom tools:\n \n+- **`mdocs`** — Run initiative/wiki maintenance commands such as `initiative.create`, `initiative.update`, `initiative.done`, `initiative.archive`, `initiative.delete`, `wiki.create`, `wiki.delete`, `wiki.list`, `validate`, and `index.sync`\n - **`mdocs_init`** — Manually initialize the `/mdocs` structure\n - **`mdocs_status`** — Show current workflow state, active initiatives, resume info (current plan item, stale warnings), and last activity\n - **`mdocs_search`** — Search across initiatives and wiki by keyword (returns snippets and matched fields)\n - **`mdocs_dispatch`** — Assemble subagent context from an initiative, its related wiki entries, search-ranked memory, and recent audit events. Includes handoff summary, blockers, progress, and retrieved memory sections.\n - **`mdocs_audit`** — Query the audit log for events (filter by initiative, type, date)\n - **`mdocs_validate`** — Validate initiative/wiki integrity, cross-link graph (broken refs, missing backlinks, completion gates)\n - **`mdocs_resume`** — Resume an initiative with next action, blockers, latest progress, and validation. Without an ID, lists all resumable initiatives with recommendations.\n - **`mdocs_lookup`** — Resolve an initiative by id, title, slug, or filename\n@@\n-| `tool` | Register `mdocs_init` and `mdocs_status` |\n+| `tool` | Register `mdocs`, `mdocs_init`, `mdocs_status`, `mdocs_validate`, `mdocs_search`, `mdocs_lookup`, `mdocs_dispatch`, `mdocs_audit`, and `mdocs_resume` |\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/test-run.js\n@@\n-if (plugin.tools && plugin.tools.mdocs_status) {\n-  const status = await plugin.tools.mdocs_status.execute();\n+if (plugin.tool && plugin.tool.mdocs_status) {\n+  const status = await plugin.tool.mdocs_status.execute();\n   console.log(`   mdocs_status returned workflow step: ${status.workflow.currentStep}`);\n   console.log(`   mdocs_status returned ${status.initiatives.length} active initiative(s)`);\n+  console.log(`   registered tools: ${Object.keys(plugin.tool).join(', ')}`);\n } else {\n   console.log('   ✗ Custom tools not found');\n }\n*** Update File: /Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/mdocs/wiki/developer/agent-implementation-guide.md\n@@\n-- **Version**: 1.0.2\n+- **Version**: 1.1.0\n*** End Patch"}}}
