{"timestamp":"2026-06-01T02:59:37.331Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"add-opencode-mdocs-to-opencode-ecosystem","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"edit","args":{"filePath":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs/mdocs/initiatives/add-index-sync-and-consistency--2026-05-29.md","oldString":"## Plan\n\n- [ ] Add INDEX consistency check to InitiativeManager\n  - Method: `checkConsistency(): { consistent: boolean, missing: string[], orphans: string[], stale: boolean }`\n  - `missing`: files listed in INDEX that don't exist on disk\n  - `orphans`: files on disk not listed in INDEX\n  - `stale`: true if any file's `updated` timestamp is newer than INDEX's last modified time\n- [ ] Add INDEX consistency check to WikiManager (same pattern)\n- [ ] Store last-sync timestamp in `mdocs/.index-meta.json`\n  - Write timestamp on every INDEX regeneration\n  - Read on checkConsistency to detect staleness\n- [ ] Add `mdocs_index_check` tool\n  - Execute: `mdocs_index_check({ mode: 'check' | 'repair' })`\n  - `mode: 'check'`: returns consistency report, does not modify files\n  - `mode: 'repair'`: regenerates INDEX files for any inconsistencies found\n  - Returns: `{ consistent: boolean, missing: [], orphans: [], repaired: boolean }`\n- [ ] Add tests for consistency check and repair modes\n- [ ] Update mdocs-workflow skill to document that direct file edits require manual INDEX sync or use `mdocs_index_check({ mode: 'repair' })`","newString":"## Plan\n\n- [ ] Add INDEX consistency check to InitiativeManager (`src/initiative.ts`)\n  - Method: `checkConsistency(): { consistent: boolean, missing: string[], orphans: string[], stale: boolean }`\n  - Parse INDEX.md to extract listed filenames\n  - `missing`: files listed in INDEX that don't exist on disk\n  - `orphans`: files on disk not listed in INDEX\n  - `stale`: true if any file's `updated` timestamp is newer than INDEX's last modified time\n- [ ] Add INDEX consistency check to WikiManager (`src/wiki.ts`)\n  - Same pattern as InitiativeManager for root INDEX.md and category indices\n- [ ] Store last-sync timestamp in `mdocs/.index-meta.json` (`src/mdocs.ts`)\n  - Write timestamp on every INDEX regeneration via InitiativeManager and WikiManager\n  - Read on checkConsistency to detect staleness\n- [ ] Add `mdocs_index_check` custom tool (`src/plugin.ts`)\n  - Execute: `mdocs_index_check({ mode: 'check' | 'repair' })`\n  - `mode: 'check'`: returns consistency report, does not modify files\n  - `mode: 'repair'`: regenerates INDEX files for any inconsistencies found\n  - Returns: `{ consistent: boolean, missing: [], orphans: [], repaired: boolean }`\n- [ ] Add tests for consistency check and repair modes (`src/__tests__/initiative.test.ts`, `src/__tests__/wiki.test.ts`)\n- [ ] Update `mdocs-workflow` SKILL.md to document direct file edit workflow"}}}
