{"timestamp":"2026-06-01T03:13:37.514Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"add-opencode-mdocs-to-opencode-ecosystem","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"bash","args":{"command":"gh release create v1.2.0 --title \"v1.2.0 — Wiki Stub Generation, Bidirectional Links, INDEX Consistency\" --notes \"## What's New\n\n### Wiki Stub Generation\n- `WikiManager.stub()` auto-creates wiki entries with default templates (Overview/Details/References)\n- `wiki.stub` and `wiki.update` commands added to the mdocs tool\n- Validation now reports broken `related_wiki` links as errors\n- Supports custom templates\n\n### Bidirectional Wiki-Initiative Links\n- Auto-generated `## Referenced By` sections in wiki entries listing all linking initiatives\n- `wiki.link` command for atomic bidirectional initiative↔wiki linking\n- `wiki.xref` command for wiki-to-wiki cross-references\n- `addRelatedInitiative()`, `getReferencedBy()`, `addWikiCrossRef()` APIs\n- `wiki.read()` returns clean content (strips auto-generated sections)\n\n### INDEX Auto-Sync and Consistency\n- `checkConsistency()` in InitiativeManager and WikiManager\n- `mdocs_index_check` custom tool with `check`/`repair` modes\n- `.index-meta.json` timestamp tracking on every index regeneration\n\n### Stats\n- 167 tests (16 new since v1.1.0)\n- 11 test suites, all passing\n- 58.1KB npm package\n\n## Commits Since v1.1.0\n- feat: add wiki stub generation and broken link validation\n- feat: add bidirectional wiki-initiative links and back-link generation\n- feat: add INDEX auto-sync and consistency utilities\n- chore(release): prepare v1.2.0\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/bbaaxx/opencode-mdocs/blob/v1.2.0/CHANGELOG.md\"","description":"Create GitHub release for v1.2.0"}}}
{"timestamp":"2026-06-01T03:13:52.807Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"add-opencode-mdocs-to-opencode-ecosystem","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"write","args":{"content":"## What's New\n\n### Wiki Stub Generation\n- `WikiManager.stub()` auto-creates wiki entries with default templates (Overview/Details/References)\n- `wiki.stub` and `wiki.update` commands added to the mdocs tool\n- Validation now reports broken `related_wiki` links as errors\n- Supports custom templates\n\n### Bidirectional Wiki-Initiative Links\n- Auto-generated `## Referenced By` sections in wiki entries listing all linking initiatives\n- `wiki.link` command for atomic bidirectional initiative↔wiki linking\n- `wiki.xref` command for wiki-to-wiki cross-references\n- `addRelatedInitiative()`, `getReferencedBy()`, `addWikiCrossRef()` APIs\n- `wiki.read()` returns clean content (strips auto-generated sections)\n\n### INDEX Auto-Sync and Consistency\n- `checkConsistency()` in InitiativeManager and WikiManager\n- `mdocs_index_check` custom tool with `check`/`repair` modes\n- `.index-meta.json` timestamp tracking on every index regeneration\n\n### Stats\n- 167 tests (16 new since v1.1.0)\n- 11 test suites, all passing\n- 58.1KB npm package\n\n## Commits Since v1.1.0\n- feat: add wiki stub generation and broken link validation\n- feat: add bidirectional wiki-initiative links and back-link generation\n- feat: add INDEX auto-sync and consistency utilities\n- chore(release): prepare v1.2.0\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/bbaaxx/opencode-mdocs/blob/v1.2.0/CHANGELOG.md\n","filePath":"/tmp/v1.2.0-release-notes.md"}}}
