{"timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:34:15.551Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"prepare-v1-3-0-release","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"bash","args":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\ntext = Path('CHANGELOG.md').read_text()\nstart = text.index('## [1.3.0]')\nrest = text[start:]\nnext_idx = rest.find('\\n## [', 1)\nnotes = rest if next_idx == -1 else rest[:next_idx]\nPath('/tmp/opencode-mdocs-v1.3.0-notes.md').write_text(notes.strip() + '\\n')\nPY\ngh release create v1.3.0 --title \"v1.3.0\" --notes-file /tmp/opencode-mdocs-v1.3.0-notes.md && gh release view v1.3.0 --json url -q .url","timeout":120000,"workdir":"/Users/bbaaxx/AgentsPlayground/opencode-mdocs","description":"Creates and verifies GitHub release"}}}
{"timestamp":"2026-06-03T19:34:24.799Z","type":"tool","initiativeId":"prepare-v1-3-0-release","step":"IDLE","details":{"toolName":"mdocs","args":{"command":"wiki.create","args":{"category":"release","id":"v1-3-0-readiness","title":"v1.3.0 Release Readiness","tags":["release","v1.3.0"],"relatedInitiatives":["prepare-v1-3-0-release"],"lifecycle":"stable","content":"## Verification Summary\n\n- **178 tests pass** across 11 suites.\n- **Build clean** (`npm run build` completes without errors).\n- **mdocs validation clean** (`mdocs_validate` reports no errors or warnings).\n- **INDEX consistency clean** (`mdocs_index_check` reports initiatives and wiki consistent).\n- **Package valid** (`npm pack` includes dist, skills, agents, templates, CHANGELOG.md, README.md, LICENSE, and package.json).\n\n## Release Summary\n\nv1.3.0 ships the PR #3 wiki orphan-warning improvements, the linked wiki INDEX consistency fix, and the runtime-only opencode plugin entrypoint fix. The CHANGELOG is the source of truth for the detailed feature and fix list.\n\n## Publish Status\n\n- [x] Git tag `v1.3.0` created and pushed\n- [x] npm: `opencode-mdocs@1.3.0` published\n- [x] GitHub release: https://github.com/bbaaxx/opencode-mdocs/releases/tag/v1.3.0\n\n## Related\n\n- **Initiative**: `prepare-v1-3-0-release`\n- **Prior release**: `release/v1-2-0-readiness`\n"}}}}
